                        "description": "C57BL/6J mice (male, 3 weeks old) were purchased from Shanghai Laboratory Animal Co Ltd. (SLAC, Shanghai, China) within one week of acclimatization. All experimental mice were housed in specific-pathogen-free (SPF) environments under a controlled condition of 12 hr light/12 hr dark cycle at 20-22 \u00b0C and 45 \u00b1 5% humidity, with free access to chow and ultrapure water. The mice were randomly divided into groups for further experiments. Body weights and food intake of all animals were recorded once a week during the experiments. Mice were fasted overnight and then anesthetized for blood harvesting. Liver, 3 types of white adipose tissues (epididymal, abdomen, and kidney adipose tissues), brown adipose tissues, and caecal content were carefully dissected and kept in liquid nitrogen before storage at -80 \u00b0C.",
